                     <id root="4fa94178-69be-1650-e063-6294a90a5e99"/>
                     <code code="50567-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="OTC - WHEN USING SECTION"/>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>avoid contact with the eyes
  <br/>
Do not use more than one patch on your body at a time
 </paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20260401"/>
                  </section>
               </component>
               <component>
                  <section ID="id_link_b865b865-881e-b07e-e053-2a95a90ae93a">
                     <id root="b865b865-881d-b07e-e053-2a95a90ae93a"/>
                     <code code="50570-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="OTC - DO NOT USE SECTION"/>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>More than one patch on your body at a time.
  <br/>
On cut, irritated or swollen skin
  <br/>
On puncture wounds
  <br/>
For more than one week without consulting a doctor
  <br/>
If you are allergic to any active or inactive ingredients
  <br/>
If pouch is damaged or opened
 </paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20210101"/>
                  </section>
               </component>
               <component>
                  <section ID="id_link_b865b1aa-5865-71d0-e053-2995a90add1a">
